perl-Religion-Islam-Quran (Holy Quran book searchable database multi-
lingual in utf-8 unicode format)

This module contains the full Holy Quran Book database searchable and
 provides many methods for retriving whole quran, specific surahs, or
 specific ayats and information about Quran and each surah in different
 languages and transliterations.

bicon is an optional dependency for Arabic console support.
